episodes.title: ABC News interviews L. Ron Hubbard's son and others about scientology
episodes.description:
This is an older news piece, but the issues remain today. MORE INFO:

Scarlett Hanna, daughter of Australia's head of scientology
talks about growing-up in Scientology on Lateline (air date: 5-18-10)
youtube [dot] com/watch?v=a73nNYiDzQY


Jenna Miscavige, niece of scientology's current leader, David Miscavige, along with several others who grew-up in the cult, launched a web site: exscientologykids [dot] org. There is a great deal of information and personal stories there.


1100 former members who have publicly spoken out with links to their personal stories:
wiki.whyweprotest [dot] net/Former_Church_of_Scientology_members_who_have_spoken_out

episodes.description: Scarlett Hanna is the daughter of Australia's head of Scientology, Vicki Dunstan. An interesting trend here as the son of the founder (L. Ron Hubbard) of scientology, Ron DeWolfe (changed his name!), as well as the brother and niece of the current international leader (David Miscavige) have also all escaped and denounced the cult.
